    "body": "### Description\n\nSince nvim 0.11 provided new LSP api, most of the LSP configs [use built-in root_markers](https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/81a570f58b2113cc2d538efae743ad38d6ab564f/lsp/lua_ls.lua#L58) field, but in gopls it's still [root_dir](https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/master/lsp/gopls.lua#L91). Is it on purpose or is it a bug?\n\nBecause in my case none of them work as it was before the migration",
